snippet.title: Curvature - Stray Wolf Boss Fight
snippet.description:
Check out this intense boss fight from the early stages of the game! You can experience it firsthand in the playable demo, now available on Steam!

Wishlist and play the demo on: https://s.team/a/2068850

Join the official discord: https://discord.gg/9T3rK43G

Follow the game on: https://twitter.com/CurvatureGame

#soulslike made by Pawel Lossew in #godot
